WEBVTT

00:00.535 --> 00:02.403
Previously on "Ghost Whisperer..."
- why do your friends shine?

00:02.471 --> 00:04.938
Because they don't have faces. they're
made of light. but they're scared.

00:05.005 --> 00:06.306
What are they scared of, buddy?

00:06.373 --> 00:09.042
- Of the shadows.
- what kind of shadows are those?

00:09.110 --> 00:11.411
The ones they make from the parts
that get left behind.

00:11.479 --> 00:13.046
- Parts of what?
- people.

00:13.114 --> 00:14.547
Broken people.

00:15.916 --> 00:17.350
I've been trying to protect you.

00:17.418 --> 00:19.018
- You and Melinda.
- Melinda?

00:19.086 --> 00:20.220
- I've said too much.
- protect her from what?

00:20.287 --> 00:21.221
Is it the shadows?

00:21.288 --> 00:22.288
Stop asking so many questions!

00:22.356 --> 00:24.324
Don't ask any questions at all.

00:24.391 --> 00:28.328
Her name's Julia Miller
and she was a patient.

00:28.395 --> 00:30.597
According to this, she lives here
at the hospital

00:30.664 --> 00:32.365
Her whole life.

00:32.433 --> 00:34.167
No one can know I'm here.

00:34.235 --> 00:35.668
- Why not?
- if they find out,

00:35.736 --> 00:38.104
- Something bad will happen.
- what?

00:38.172 --> 00:40.707
Something really bad.

00:40.774 --> 00:42.775
[wind blowing]

00:44.000 --> 00:50.074
